---
title: Quick Double Herby Chicken & Cheesy Veggie Couscous with Lemon Mayo Drizzle
description: Tonight, we’ve got fragrant chicken sprinkled with herbs and garlic and it’s calling our name. We’re going to answer that call with a colourful couscous, popping with veggies and a sprinkling of Parmesan cheese. When it all combines, you’re in for an explosion of flavour!

*We’ve replaced the couscous in this recipe with pearl couscous due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just
as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
